OL,5, A passenger sent bailiffs to Luton     
OL,6, Airport to confront Wizz Air over money
OL,7, owed to him after his family's flights 
OL,8, were cancelled at the last minute.     
OL,10,FRussell Quirk said he was left with    
OL,11,Flittle choice but to find another route
OL,12,Fto Portugal which cost him #4,500.     
OL,14,FAfter months of waiting for Wizz Air   
OL,15,Freimbursement, he went to court and    
OL,16,Fended up sending in the bailiffs.      
OL,18,FWizz Air paid up, apologised and said  
OL,19,Fit "fell short of our own aspirations  
OL,20,Fand our customers' expectations".      
